citation: Proclamation under the Government Procurement Review (International Free Trade Agreements) Act 2019 (Tas)
text:
Proclamation under the Government Procurement Review (International Free Trade Agreements) Act 2019

I, the Governor in and over the State of Tasmania and its Dependencies in the Commonwealth of Australia, acting with the advice of the Executive Council, by this my proclamation made under section 2 of the Government Procurement Review (International Free Trade Agreements) Act 2019 fix 21 February 2020 as the day on which that Act commences.

28 January 2020

C. WARNER

Governor

By Her Excellency's Command,

PETER GUTWEIN

Treasurer

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 5 February 2020

This proclamation is administered in the Department of Treasury and Finance.
